    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows some noticeable scuffs and minor paint fading in certain areas, consistent with regular use over the years. Inside, the upholstery exhibits some wear and minor staining, though all essential controls and features remain fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound and has been maintained to ensure it starts reliably and handles well on the road. It is a solid choice for a buyer looking for a budget-friendly, practical vehicle that prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
