    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and carefully maintained, so it\u2019s totally ready for all your upcoming road trips and daily commutes. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin\u2014I know you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, ensuring direct mechanical engagement. The VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been inspected and reinforced. The chassis remains taut with updated polyurethane bushings and factory-spec dampers. Power is delivered through the Variable M Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains exceptionally healthy, exhibiting strong compression and smooth throttle response via its individual throttle bodies.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
