    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Lexus RX 350 in a sophisticated Pearl White finish. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep gloss, though there is a minor, professionally touched-up stone chip on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from city parking\u2014hardly noticeable but mentioned for full transparency. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is in beautiful shape, free of any tears, odors, or stains. All premium features, including the heated and ventilated seats, panoramic sunroof, and the 12.3-inch navigation display, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this SUV is sound; it has been serviced every 5,000 miles at the local dealership, and I have the full service history logs available for your review. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced just last month. It drives as smoothly as the day it was bought. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
